obstacles: `o_dark`, `o_battery`
</div>

<div class="beflix-stage" data-prog="su_light_darkness"></div>

<div class="past">PAST: the underground already contains darkness as a predator; earlier bodies failed where light failed.</div>

<div class="present">PRESENT: the lamp burns down while the adventurer chooses routes, carrying finite safety through rooms that erase the map.</div>

<div class="future">FUTURE: permanent torchlight or death by grue; every delay becomes visible as battery loss.</div>

ABC seed: light is not decoration; it is a consumable body. The film watches the lamp become time. (Toggle LIT off: the room is erased — `CLR 7`. Toggle GRUE: the terminal.)

