# SU 12 — Machine / Diamond

<div class="legos-card">
LEGOS atoms:

locations: `loc_machine`, `loc_drafty`  
entities: `ent_coal`, `ent_screw`, `t_diamond`  
goals: `g_diamond`  
shifts: `sh_diamond`
</div>

<div class="beflix-stage" data-prog="su_machine_diamond"></div>

<div class="past">PAST: the machine preserves empire technology as an idle transformation engine.</div>

<div class="present">PRESENT: coal is inserted; the screwdriver activates the switch; pressure converts material state.</div>

<div class="future">FUTURE: coal becomes diamond; industrial action becomes treasure.</div>

ABC seed: black mineral enters a machine and returns as compressed light. (PRESS closes the machine — the SEAM.)

<div class="nav">[[prev->SU 11 Mine Gas Basket]] · [[next->SU 13 Loud Room]]</div>

:: SU 13 Loud Room [state-unit] {"position":"3620,170","size":"240,180"}
# SU 13 — Loud Room

<div class="legos-card">
LEGOS atoms:

locations: `loc_loud`  
entities: `t_bar`  
obstacles: `o_loud`  
shifts: `sh_echo`
</div>

<div class="beflix-stage" data-prog="su_loud_room"></div>

<div class="past">PAST: the room has turned language into uncontrolled repetition.</div>

<div class="present">PRESENT: the command `echo` names the room's behavior and cancels it.</div>

<div class="future">FUTURE: sound quiets; the platinum bar becomes obtainable.</div>

ABC seed: a room that repeats commands is silenced when it hears its own mechanism named. (ECHO quiets the room and reveals the bar.)

<div class="nav">[[prev->SU 12 Machine Diamond]] · [[next->SU 14 Trophy Endgame]]</div>

:: SU 14 Trophy Endgame [state-unit] {"position":"3900,170","size":"240,180"}
# SU 14 — Trophy / Endgame

<div class="legos-card">
LEGOS atoms:

locations: `loc_living`, `loc_stone_barrow`  
entities: `ent_case`, all treasures  
goals: `g_case`, `g_master`  
shifts: `sh_win`
</div>

<div class="beflix-stage" data-prog="su_trophy_endgame"></div>

<div class="past">PAST: the trophy case has waited as an empty grammar for recovered empire objects.</div>

<div class="present">PRESENT: each treasure is deposited; the house becomes a ledger of solved transformations.</div>

<div class="future">FUTURE: the final treasure produces a map to the Stone Barrow; completion opens the next game.</div>

ABC seed: the opening room returns transformed; the ordinary case becomes a portal because every object now carries a solved past. (FILL CASE flips to the WIN state — Stone Barrow map.)

